WEBVTT

01:32.080 --> 01:34.990
[How dare you!?]

01:35.039 --> 01:37.960
[Episode 27]

01:47.789 --> 01:48.650
Your Highness,

01:48.950 --> 01:50.870
His Majesty prepared these clothes
beforehand

01:50.870 --> 01:52.430
for us to conceal our identities.

01:52.430 --> 01:53.690
Let me help you change.

01:54.560 --> 01:56.590
When did he start planning all this?

02:00.760 --> 02:01.620
Your Highness,

02:02.400 --> 02:03.590
please eat something.

02:03.590 --> 02:05.120
We need to hit the road soon.

02:05.280 --> 02:06.210
I'm not leaving.

02:09.080 --> 02:11.680
We'll return to the palace
at the crack of dawn.

02:12.560 --> 02:13.630
By His Majesty's decree,

02:13.630 --> 02:15.100
if Your Highness asks to return,

02:15.100 --> 02:16.900
we can use our lives as leverage.

02:23.230 --> 02:25.360
He knows I won't take an innocent life,

02:27.910 --> 02:29.710
so he devised this tactic for me.

02:33.190 --> 02:33.520
Fine.

02:36.520 --> 02:37.650
You are all free now.

02:39.400 --> 02:40.600
Let's part ways here.

02:44.870 --> 02:45.730
Your Highness!

02:47.800 --> 02:48.240
What?

02:49.400 --> 02:50.800
Are you going to tie me up?

02:51.120 --> 02:52.120
Your Highness...

02:53.870 --> 02:54.800
Upon departure,

02:54.970 --> 02:56.970
His Majesty left me with this letter

02:57.870 --> 03:01.400
and asked me to give it to Your Highness
after we escaped danger.

03:01.560 --> 03:03.310
But now I'm taking the liberty
to present it

03:03.310 --> 03:04.370
ahead of schedule.

03:06.000 --> 03:07.930
Your Highness, please read it over

03:07.960 --> 03:09.420
before making a decision.

03:14.680 --> 03:15.940
To my dear wife Wanyin:

03:16.710 --> 03:18.110
My real name is Zhang San.

03:20.310 --> 03:21.360
Laugh if you want.

03:22.560 --> 03:24.160
In the past, I was often asked

03:24.310 --> 03:25.520
why my parents gave me

03:26.079 --> 03:27.610
such an unremarkable name.

03:28.400 --> 03:30.190
But the reality was quite the opposite.

03:30.190 --> 03:32.110
From elementary to middle school,

03:32.110 --> 03:32.750
I was always the first student

03:32.750 --> 03:34.960
whose name was remembered by the teachers.

03:34.960 --> 03:37.350
[Zhang San]

03:35.560 --> 03:36.190
However,

03:36.870 --> 03:38.530
except for this unusual name,

03:39.210 --> 03:40.340
everything about me

03:40.500 --> 03:41.960
actually seemed lackluster.

03:41.960 --> 03:45.470
[SOS]

03:42.680 --> 03:44.340
I was only an average student.

03:48.590 --> 03:50.850
At this point, you might start wondering

03:51.430 --> 03:54.430
why I keep talking about my time
in junior high school.

03:55.430 --> 03:56.690
That's because my life

03:57.790 --> 03:59.790
in the world we're from ended there.

04:01.190 --> 04:02.050
In ninth grade,

04:02.590 --> 04:04.920
when I was fiddling with my phone
in class,

04:05.030 --> 04:06.240
ia pop-up add

04:07.190 --> 04:08.590
sucked me into this book.

04:09.960 --> 04:12.430
It has been 16 years and 8 months
since then.

04:14.960 --> 04:16.019
Come to think of it,

04:17.040 --> 04:19.240
I've been playing the role of Xiahou Dan

04:20.269 --> 04:22.930
for a longer time
than I spent on being Zhang San.

04:23.720 --> 04:28.480
Long live Your Majesty!

04:29.800 --> 04:31.000
In the past two years,

04:31.430 --> 04:33.560
sometimes a doubt would cross my mind—

04:33.950 --> 04:35.680
did that world outside the book

04:35.800 --> 04:36.680
truly exist,

04:38.190 --> 04:41.250
or was it just an illusion
created within my sick brain?

04:43.310 --> 04:44.570
You know what's funny?

04:45.480 --> 04:46.680
When I first arrived,

04:47.430 --> 04:48.830
I felt like I was trapped

04:48.830 --> 04:50.490
in a never-ending nightmare.

04:51.270 --> 04:52.530
But now in retrospect,

04:53.480 --> 04:54.630
I can barely recall the name

04:54.630 --> 04:56.030
of my junior high school.

04:57.750 --> 04:59.409
It all changed when you asked,

05:00.040 --> 05:00.600
"How

05:01.390 --> 05:01.870
are

05:02.270 --> 05:02.830
you?"

05:04.070 --> 05:06.070
I finally realized my past was true,

05:08.030 --> 05:08.830
and that I had

05:09.310 --> 05:10.510
had a real life.

05:11.870 --> 05:12.930
I once had parents,

05:13.560 --> 05:14.390
friends,

05:15.360 --> 05:16.190
and a future.

05:19.430 --> 05:20.890
I'm such a despicable man.

05:21.720 --> 05:23.520
You saved me at that very moment,

05:23.920 --> 05:25.180
yet in the next second,

05:25.920 --> 05:27.650
I devised a plan to deceive you,

05:28.430 --> 05:29.780
to gain your trust,

05:30.960 --> 05:32.090
to become your ally,

05:33.720 --> 05:35.850
and to use your knowledge of the script

05:36.040 --> 05:37.100
for my own benefit.

05:38.360 --> 05:39.360
Only through that

05:40.360 --> 05:42.620
could I achieve victory in the surest way

05:43.510 --> 05:45.570
and retaliate on the Empress Dowager

05:45.720 --> 05:46.920
and Prince Duan.

05:48.110 --> 05:49.310
Don't worry, CEO Dan.

05:50.000 --> 05:52.000
We're in the same boat to begin with.

05:52.159 --> 05:54.220
I'll stick with you till the very end.

05:54.800 --> 05:55.659
In front of you,

05:56.750 --> 05:58.680
I've not only glossed over my past,

05:59.630 --> 06:02.430
but also carefully watched
my manners and speech,

06:03.160 --> 06:03.870
trying to act like

06:03.870 --> 06:06.000
a modern person you're familiar with.

06:15.040 --> 06:16.550
So what if you're the Emperor?

06:16.550 --> 06:18.210
Can you protect her from harm?

06:18.920 --> 06:19.650
That I can do.

06:19.990 --> 06:21.070
Then can you guarantee

06:21.070 --> 06:23.430
that among all the women in the world,
she'll be the only one you want?

06:23.430 --> 06:24.430
That's also easy.

06:26.170 --> 06:27.240
As Zhang San,

06:28.090 --> 06:30.350
loving you seems to be a matter of course.

06:31.800 --> 06:32.800
But as Xiahou Dan,

06:34.000 --> 06:35.460
it's practically insane.

06:36.630 --> 06:39.290
I can't tell
when exactly I fell in love with you.

06:39.750 --> 06:41.150
The only thing I'm sure of

06:41.290 --> 06:42.820
is that I became more afraid

06:43.960 --> 06:45.890
of exposing the truth thereafter.

06:48.420 --> 06:48.880
Wanyin,

06:50.040 --> 06:51.170
believe it or not,

06:52.480 --> 06:54.080
only when I reverted to being

06:55.190 --> 06:57.390
Zhang San from Xiahou Dan in front of you

06:59.190 --> 07:01.190
did it occur to me, little by little,

07:01.950 --> 07:04.880
that how far I had drifted
from my original identity.

07:06.000 --> 07:07.260
You came here too late,

07:07.480 --> 07:07.960
Wanyin.

07:08.250 --> 07:09.240
♪ Tell me ♪

07:09.900 --> 07:13.360
♪ Why so many laments echo in the wind ♪

07:09.920 --> 07:12.450
There isn't a fellow of yours
waiting for you.

07:13.680 --> 07:14.970
You have to stuck with me,

07:14.970 --> 07:16.120
♪ Walk past me ♪

07:15.040 --> 07:16.510
a crazy dying man.

07:16.420 --> 07:20.300
♪ Like an aloof passerby ♪

07:20.830 --> 07:21.630
Those who are drowning

07:21.510 --> 07:24.050
♪ Don't watch me as the rain falls ♪

07:22.040 --> 07:23.920
all wish for a piece of driftwood.

07:24.800 --> 07:27.640
♪ Love burns too hot as it passes ♪

07:24.840 --> 07:26.840
But when they are too far from shore,

07:26.920 --> 07:28.370
they're destined for doom.

07:28.370 --> 07:34.230
♪ Even a lifetime of war
cannot be extinguished ♪

07:29.040 --> 07:30.770
By holding onto the driftwood,

07:31.080 --> 07:32.630
they will only end up dragging it

07:32.630 --> 07:33.960
down into the water too.

07:34.310 --> 07:36.020
You shouldn't let love

07:35.180 --> 07:36.400
♪ Blame me ♪

07:36.360 --> 07:37.360
cloud your judgement.

07:36.970 --> 07:40.570
♪ For the frailty of fate ♪

07:38.570 --> 07:40.700
She's driftwood to me, a drowning man.

07:41.290 --> 07:41.930
I hope I can

07:42.030 --> 07:43.310
♪ Hide me ♪

07:42.840 --> 07:44.650
at least keep your hands free of blood.

07:43.720 --> 07:47.630
♪ With light snow or thick ink ♪

07:45.750 --> 07:46.880
In this living hell,

07:48.240 --> 07:49.420
there should at least be a place

07:48.920 --> 07:51.510
♪ We met in the crowd ♪

07:50.750 --> 07:52.330
for you to have a sound sleep.

07:52.330 --> 07:54.930
♪ There's no mistake in this life ♪

07:52.810 --> 07:54.170
[Taiji Hall]

07:53.610 --> 07:54.360
All I beg for

07:55.750 --> 07:56.750
is to delay facing

07:55.820 --> 07:58.810
♪ I only regret being clumsy in words ♪

07:57.750 --> 07:59.280
the fear and wariness in your eyes.

07:58.860 --> 08:01.030
♪ And shrinking from speaking it out ♪

08:00.310 --> 08:01.310
I wish for nothing

08:01.370 --> 08:03.750
♪ Even when destiny mocked me, hurt me ♪

08:02.920 --> 08:04.560
but to see you always thriving
like burning fire

08:03.810 --> 08:05.680
♪ Destroyed me, or trapped me ♪

08:05.560 --> 08:06.510
and shining like the moon.

08:05.710 --> 08:08.180
♪ I never yielded ♪

08:07.270 --> 08:08.270
We need to play

08:08.460 --> 08:09.960
♪ But why ♪

08:08.600 --> 08:09.630
a game of survival overtime.

08:09.630 --> 08:11.160
I hope you will remain to be the brave

08:10.220 --> 08:14.660
♪ Can't I bear to see
even a single tear in your eyes? ♪

08:11.310 --> 08:12.600
and fearless young lady

08:12.600 --> 08:14.130
who I met in the first place.

08:14.360 --> 08:15.240
Punch the Empress Dowager

08:15.140 --> 08:17.510
♪ But we once fell in love, went wild ♪

08:15.430 --> 08:16.510
and kick Prince Duan!

08:16.510 --> 08:17.680
Even if he were truly a god,

08:17.560 --> 08:19.360
♪ Split up, and lost each other ♪

08:18.480 --> 08:19.920
I would never surrender!

08:19.430 --> 08:21.740
♪ They are
all unforgettable memories to me ♪

08:20.310 --> 08:21.110
Let's get him!

08:21.430 --> 08:22.310
I am not alone on this path!

08:22.100 --> 08:23.980
♪ The first time I met you ♪

08:22.850 --> 08:23.360
Wanyin,

08:24.190 --> 08:25.310
I no longer have a place to call home.

08:24.330 --> 08:33.740
♪ It felt like something suddenly
lit up my soul ♪

08:26.750 --> 08:28.410
But in you, I've found my home.

08:29.510 --> 08:31.060
If you ever fear and waiver,

08:32.140 --> 08:34.270
or need support from a fellow of yours,

08:35.409 --> 08:36.870
I'll gladly play that role

08:37.960 --> 08:38.630
till the day

08:39.909 --> 08:41.020
my life is over.

08:41.510 --> 08:42.510
I beg you, Mr. Bei,

08:43.080 --> 08:43.740
to treat her

08:44.360 --> 08:45.360
as you'd treat me.

08:45.860 --> 08:47.210
Please ensure her safety at all costs.

08:47.210 --> 08:48.410
♪ Blame me ♪

08:47.360 --> 08:48.490
What I didn't expect

08:48.580 --> 08:50.230
was that this day would come so soon.

08:49.040 --> 08:52.540
♪ For the frailty of fate ♪

08:52.660 --> 08:54.160
I will try my best tomorrow.

08:54.160 --> 08:55.220
♪ Hide me ♪

08:54.670 --> 08:55.510
If I succeed,

08:55.900 --> 08:59.700
♪ With light snow or thick ink ♪

08:57.320 --> 08:58.250
the burden on you

08:58.440 --> 08:59.370
will be lighter.

09:00.840 --> 09:01.720
If I fail,

09:01.030 --> 09:03.450
♪ We met in the crowd ♪

09:03.320 --> 09:05.240
do as the final page says.

09:04.310 --> 09:06.920
♪ There's no mistake in this life ♪

09:07.430 --> 09:08.680
You should be able to make an escape
that way.

09:07.870 --> 09:10.850
♪ I only regret being clumsy in words ♪

09:10.380 --> 09:11.330
Then you will have to

09:10.870 --> 09:13.020
♪ And shrinking from speaking it out ♪

09:12.730 --> 09:13.940
tread the road ahead alone.

09:13.440 --> 09:15.860
♪ Even when destiny mocked me, hurt me ♪

09:15.910 --> 09:17.670
♪ Destroyed me, or trapped me ♪

09:17.510 --> 09:18.480
It's going to be a long

09:17.700 --> 09:20.220
♪ I never yielded ♪

09:19.750 --> 09:20.630
and dangerous journey.

09:20.530 --> 09:22.050
♪ But why ♪

09:21.790 --> 09:22.510
Be extra careful.

09:22.260 --> 09:26.750
♪ Can't I bear to see
even a single tear in your eyes? ♪

09:24.790 --> 09:26.050
I'm sorry for not being

09:26.670 --> 09:27.400
a good enough person.

09:27.160 --> 09:29.520
♪ But we once fell in love, went wild ♪

09:28.870 --> 09:30.350
Though I've lied to you many times,

09:29.560 --> 09:31.410
♪ Split up, and lost each other ♪

09:31.450 --> 09:33.780
♪ They are
all unforgettable memories to me ♪

09:32.320 --> 09:33.050
this apology

09:34.250 --> 09:35.950
♪ The first time I met you ♪

09:34.420 --> 09:35.550
is genuine and true.

09:36.540 --> 09:39.470
♪ There was once light ♪

09:37.760 --> 09:39.480
You're the bravest

09:40.060 --> 09:48.460
♪ In my soul ♪

09:42.370 --> 09:44.100
and the most formidable person

09:45.550 --> 09:46.880
I've met in my two lives.

09:48.780 --> 09:50.980
You'll definitely have the last laugh,

09:51.030 --> 09:52.030
fighting your way

09:52.840 --> 09:54.040
to a bright new world.

09:54.540 --> 09:56.960
♪ Even when destiny mocked me, hurt me ♪

09:55.370 --> 09:56.080
By then,

09:57.010 --> 09:58.770
♪ Destroyed me, or trapped me ♪

09:57.440 --> 09:58.800
should you have forgiven me,

09:58.800 --> 10:01.380
♪ I never yielded ♪

09:59.720 --> 10:00.780
just enjoy a hot pot

10:01.520 --> 10:02.960
on holidays and festivals,

10:01.620 --> 10:03.140
♪ But why ♪

10:03.400 --> 10:08.020
♪ Can't I bear to see
even a single tear in your eyes? ♪

10:05.330 --> 10:06.790
as if I were there with you.

10:08.340 --> 10:10.690
♪ But we once fell in love, went wild ♪

10:08.750 --> 10:09.680
From: Zhang San.

10:10.720 --> 10:12.570
♪ Split up, and lost each other ♪

10:12.610 --> 10:14.940
♪ They are
all unforgettable memories to me ♪

10:15.410 --> 10:17.190
♪ The first time I met you ♪

10:17.710 --> 10:25.590
♪ It felt like something suddenly
lit up my soul ♪

10:37.200 --> 10:37.790
Hurry up.

10:38.080 --> 10:39.120
His Majesty suddenly fell ill.

10:39.120 --> 10:40.240
Physicians, please be quick!

10:40.240 --> 10:40.870
Sure, sure.

10:40.870 --> 10:41.270
Got it.

10:50.540 --> 10:52.000
Move faster, physicians.

10:54.120 --> 10:54.960
My leg!

10:58.720 --> 10:59.120
Hurry!

11:10.000 --> 11:10.840
It's not His Majesty.

11:10.840 --> 11:11.300
This...

11:11.480 --> 11:12.540
is not His Majesty.

11:13.030 --> 11:14.490
Say that again, I dare you!

11:17.030 --> 11:18.630
What are you all waiting for?

11:19.390 --> 11:21.020
Come fix my leg right now!

11:21.720 --> 11:22.390
Yes, yes.

11:23.050 --> 11:23.820
Quick!

11:37.230 --> 11:38.090
Your Highness,

11:38.670 --> 11:40.360
Chu Si scouted the gate tower at night

11:40.360 --> 11:42.960
and found the Imperial Guards
to be led by Prince Duan's men.

11:42.960 --> 11:43.390
Now,

11:43.750 --> 11:46.280
the city gate is surrounded
by border troops.

11:48.030 --> 11:49.430
As for where we should go,

11:49.440 --> 11:50.840
it's up to Your Highness.

11:52.000 --> 11:53.260
How are your injuries?

11:54.030 --> 11:55.090
These minor wounds

11:55.270 --> 11:56.330
amount to nothing.

11:59.200 --> 12:00.600
Let's leave the mountain

12:00.960 --> 12:02.320
for an inhabited area.

12:03.550 --> 12:05.190
Or we can't receive news
about the capital.

12:05.190 --> 12:07.030
I'm here to protect Your Highness
by imperial order.

12:07.030 --> 12:08.510
There are many uncertainties now.

12:08.510 --> 12:10.030
The troops from three border regions
arranged by Prince Duan

12:10.030 --> 12:11.270
are closing in on this place

12:11.270 --> 12:12.440
to suppress the Imperial Guards

12:12.440 --> 12:14.040
and help him take the throne.

12:14.750 --> 12:15.490
These troops

12:15.870 --> 12:18.490
are coming from the north, east and south.

12:18.520 --> 12:19.240
I suggest

12:19.960 --> 12:21.100
we find a way out

12:21.550 --> 12:22.840
before they join forces.

12:22.840 --> 12:23.840
Let's head south.

12:24.210 --> 12:25.070
Your Highness,

12:25.270 --> 12:27.470
the Right Army is coming from the south.

12:27.510 --> 12:28.440
We'll head south

12:29.080 --> 12:29.740
to Peiyang.

12:31.200 --> 12:32.930
That's what His Majesty wants.

12:35.320 --> 12:37.250
Clothes were prepared beforehand, right?

12:37.250 --> 12:38.110
Put them on now.

12:38.960 --> 12:39.870
Then we'll set out.

12:39.870 --> 12:40.200
Yes.

12:40.200 --> 12:40.510
Yes.

13:32.870 --> 13:33.390
Sir,

13:33.740 --> 13:35.470
did you sell fish in town today?

13:35.670 --> 13:36.190
Yes.

13:36.330 --> 13:37.630
The business wasn't good,

13:37.630 --> 13:38.760
so I came back early.

13:40.080 --> 13:40.510
Ma'am,

13:40.870 --> 13:42.070
is your husband home?

13:42.120 --> 13:42.750
Yes, he is.

13:44.550 --> 13:46.480
There's a huge manhunt in town now.

13:46.510 --> 13:48.200
It's said to be complete chaos.

13:48.200 --> 13:49.400
How weird and creepy.

13:50.150 --> 13:53.340
Why would so many people die
during the Empress Dowager's funeral?

13:53.340 --> 13:54.670
Could it be possible that Her Majesty

13:54.670 --> 13:55.990
tried to take people with her

13:55.990 --> 13:58.240
to the nether world
so she could have servants there?

13:58.240 --> 13:59.370
But as I heard, it was

13:59.440 --> 14:00.870
the demonic consort
who murdered the Empress Dowager

14:00.870 --> 14:01.750
and planned to kill

14:01.750 --> 14:03.240
the Emperor too during the funeral.

14:03.240 --> 14:04.280
Is that true?

14:05.030 --> 14:06.670
There are wanted posters for her
at the city gate now.

14:06.670 --> 14:08.600
-Really?
-It can't be fake, can it?

14:11.080 --> 14:11.680
Excuse me.

14:12.630 --> 14:14.910
My sisters and I are heading
to the capital to meet our kin.

14:14.910 --> 14:17.040
We just overheard your conversation.

14:17.480 --> 14:18.490
Is it safe to go

14:18.670 --> 14:19.730
to the capital now?

14:20.200 --> 14:21.260
At a time like this,

14:21.960 --> 14:23.000
even a strong male like me

14:23.000 --> 14:24.530
dare not enter the capital.

14:24.600 --> 14:25.940
Young ladies, I suggest

14:26.240 --> 14:27.500
you make a second plan.

14:31.270 --> 14:32.600
Right now, entry to the capital

14:32.600 --> 14:34.330
is allowed, but exit is denied.

14:34.870 --> 14:36.960
My husband went there to sell fish
early in the day,

14:36.960 --> 14:38.870
and is still trapped within till now.

14:38.870 --> 14:40.730
But this gentleman here just said

14:41.080 --> 14:43.340
the manhunt was for the demonic consort.

14:43.390 --> 14:44.390
Why are even males

14:45.240 --> 14:47.240
forbidden to leave the capital now?

14:48.270 --> 14:49.150
Who knows?

14:49.870 --> 14:51.130
Come on. Let's go home.

14:58.000 --> 14:58.720
Could it be

14:59.670 --> 15:01.270
that Xiahou Dan has escaped?

15:16.440 --> 15:16.870
-Your Highness.
-Your Highness!

15:16.870 --> 15:17.200
Your Highness!

15:17.200 --> 15:18.130
Are you alright?

15:19.720 --> 15:20.780
You're burning up.

15:21.080 --> 15:22.410
We can't go any further.

15:22.510 --> 15:24.480
Her Highness needs to take a rest
somewhere.

15:24.480 --> 15:25.630
I'll check out on that house.

15:25.630 --> 15:26.160
Don't.

15:26.690 --> 15:28.620
Commoners dread strange men most.

15:29.150 --> 15:30.610
And there are so many of us.

15:30.870 --> 15:32.270
Chu Wu, you do it instead.

15:32.510 --> 15:33.310
The two of you,

15:33.600 --> 15:34.860
go hide somewhere.

15:38.550 --> 15:38.910
Take care of Her Highness.

15:38.910 --> 15:39.240
Sure.

15:42.840 --> 15:43.370
Let's go.

15:52.250 --> 15:52.840
Sir,

15:53.000 --> 15:55.270
we plan to visit our relatives
in the capital.

15:55.270 --> 15:57.200
Yet our money was stolen on the way.

15:57.360 --> 15:59.220
Now, the lady of our house is sick.

16:01.030 --> 16:02.890
This is all the money we have on us.

16:03.120 --> 16:05.050
Could you kindly give us some food?

16:05.200 --> 16:06.730
We're all suffering souls.

16:07.270 --> 16:08.140
Come on in.

16:09.790 --> 16:10.320
Let's go.

16:13.600 --> 16:14.200
Thank you.

16:27.030 --> 16:28.090
Why is your wife...

16:29.000 --> 16:29.800
burning that?

16:31.270 --> 16:33.800
To mourn her brother
who lived near Mount Bei.

16:34.080 --> 16:34.870
Yesterday,

16:35.440 --> 16:36.910
while he was taking a peek

16:37.150 --> 16:39.080
at the Empress Dowager's funeral,

16:39.720 --> 16:40.580
unexpectedly,

16:41.120 --> 16:42.850
Prince Duan rose in a rebellion

16:43.440 --> 16:44.770
and caused many deaths.

16:44.790 --> 16:47.050
My wife's brother somehow lost his life.

16:47.720 --> 16:49.580
Prince Duan started a rebellion?

16:51.150 --> 16:52.080
Was it a success?

16:52.200 --> 16:52.750
W-We...

16:53.150 --> 16:54.550
have no idea at all.

16:55.120 --> 16:56.790
He who delivered the bad news to us

16:56.790 --> 16:58.320
just said many people died,

16:58.600 --> 17:00.550
most of which were Imperial Guards.

17:00.550 --> 17:02.720
He didn't know much other than that.

17:04.640 --> 17:06.770
The dead were mostly Imperial Guards.

17:06.960 --> 17:08.609
There was either an internal fight
within them,

17:08.609 --> 17:10.740
or that Prince Duan veiled his armies.

17:10.880 --> 17:11.740
In either case,

17:12.640 --> 17:14.420
CEO Dan must've got in grave danger.

17:14.420 --> 17:14.880
My Lady.

17:15.310 --> 17:15.750
Sir,

17:16.680 --> 17:18.270
we shouldn't bother you
at a time like this,

17:18.270 --> 17:19.920
but the lady of our house is severely ill.

17:19.920 --> 17:21.440
Could you make her a bowl of noodles?

17:21.440 --> 17:22.240
Wait a moment.

17:22.400 --> 17:23.030
My love,

17:23.480 --> 17:24.740
make some noodles now.

17:27.680 --> 17:28.210
Let's go.

17:39.830 --> 17:40.440
Here you are.

17:40.440 --> 17:41.500
Have some noodles.

17:42.160 --> 17:42.760
Thank you.

17:44.000 --> 17:44.400
Take it.

17:44.400 --> 17:45.030
Thanks.

17:52.590 --> 17:53.450
Your Highness,

17:53.880 --> 17:55.010
at least have a bite.

17:55.590 --> 17:56.920
A long journey awaits us.

17:56.920 --> 17:57.720
That's right.

17:57.920 --> 17:59.590
Travel takes physical strength.

17:59.590 --> 18:00.850
Please eat something.

18:02.200 --> 18:03.000
You're right.

18:05.440 --> 18:06.440
I can't fall now.

18:07.350 --> 18:08.810
He's still waiting for me.

18:11.110 --> 18:12.170
You should eat too.

18:12.680 --> 18:13.030
Yes.

18:22.480 --> 18:23.740
Alright, stop crying.

18:24.110 --> 18:25.480
It's bad for your eyes.

18:26.070 --> 18:28.070
I just pity my unfortunate brother.

18:31.030 --> 18:33.630
That heinous Prince Duan
is beneath contempt!

18:35.200 --> 18:36.440
Keep it down.

18:39.720 --> 18:42.000
First,
the Emperor killed the Empress Dowager.

18:42.000 --> 18:45.200
Then, Prince Duan rebelled
and tried to kill the Emperor.

18:45.480 --> 18:46.010
These...

18:46.830 --> 18:48.300
are all royal affairs.

18:48.480 --> 18:50.110
How could we have foreseen those?

18:50.110 --> 18:51.640
It's true I don't know much,

18:51.720 --> 18:52.520
but my brother

18:52.640 --> 18:53.310
told me...

18:54.070 --> 18:56.270
that the Emperor ordered
equal land distribution

18:56.270 --> 18:57.330
and tax reduction.

18:57.480 --> 19:00.340
His Majesty also executed
many corrupt officials!

19:00.720 --> 19:03.110
Isn't it enough to put
these corrupt officials in jail?

19:03.110 --> 19:04.110
Why execute them?

19:05.240 --> 19:07.240
If I am to have the people's support,

19:07.720 --> 19:09.250
I must first give them hope.

19:09.270 --> 19:10.730
Execution is a just desert

19:11.240 --> 19:12.700
for these vile officials.

19:14.440 --> 19:15.970
It gives hope to the people.

19:16.750 --> 19:17.510
Back then,

19:18.390 --> 19:20.650
I thought he was just acting over the top.

19:20.830 --> 19:21.960
Little did I imagine

19:22.720 --> 19:25.180
that after living for 16 years
in this world,

19:25.640 --> 19:28.100
he had already seen
the harsh truths of life.

19:29.240 --> 19:30.570
Sacrificing one person

19:31.310 --> 19:32.840
to ensure others' survival

19:33.310 --> 19:34.590
is sometimes unavoidable.

19:34.590 --> 19:35.550
Don't you forget

19:36.270 --> 19:37.600
they are 2D characters.

19:38.110 --> 19:39.730
I would also remind myself

19:41.140 --> 19:43.200
not to get too emotionally involved.

19:43.240 --> 19:45.240
Do you really think you are a tyrant?

19:45.270 --> 19:46.720
I am a tyrant,

19:47.510 --> 19:48.980
as I have always been.

19:50.550 --> 19:52.550
But the man who claimed to be a tyrant

19:53.200 --> 19:55.370
and to have no regard for others' lives

19:55.790 --> 19:57.440
is actually spending what little

19:57.440 --> 19:58.590
time and life he has

19:59.400 --> 20:00.350
to protect

20:00.350 --> 20:02.410
all those irrelevant 2D characters.

20:08.640 --> 20:09.500
Your Highness,

20:09.640 --> 20:10.240
don't cry.

20:21.440 --> 20:22.750
What's with this lady?

20:23.680 --> 20:26.410
Perhaps she's missing
her family in the capital.

20:28.400 --> 20:30.000
Life hasn't treated us well.

20:30.510 --> 20:31.110
Dear,

20:31.720 --> 20:33.320
let me get you some more soup.

20:33.640 --> 20:35.970
You won't feel homesick on a full stomach.

20:37.240 --> 20:38.240
Thank you, ma'am.

20:39.550 --> 20:40.880
But I can't eat anymore.

20:44.380 --> 20:45.780
Why is your face so red?

20:47.670 --> 20:48.960
She's running a high fever.

20:48.960 --> 20:50.680
We need to get her a physician now.

20:50.680 --> 20:51.350
Honey!

20:51.590 --> 20:52.120
I'm fine.

20:53.000 --> 20:54.800
I'm just tired from the journey.

20:55.830 --> 20:57.630
Could we stay here for the night?

21:00.440 --> 21:02.100
We don't mean to turn you down,

21:02.720 --> 21:04.980
but the authorities have issued a notice

21:05.350 --> 21:07.550
forbidding residents
from housing strangers

21:07.550 --> 21:08.270
overnight.

21:09.790 --> 21:11.070
Although you're not bad people,

21:11.070 --> 21:11.790
ladies,

21:12.590 --> 21:14.220
we common folks

21:14.510 --> 21:16.570
dare not go against the authorities.

21:17.110 --> 21:17.840
How about...

21:20.750 --> 21:21.550
In that case,

21:22.830 --> 21:24.030
we'll take our leave.

21:24.880 --> 21:26.340
Thank you for the noodles.

21:32.920 --> 21:33.520
Thank you.

21:46.750 --> 21:47.070
That...

21:47.070 --> 21:48.000
What's going on?

21:48.030 --> 21:48.490
This...

21:56.680 --> 21:57.140
Well...

21:59.000 --> 21:59.660
Quiet down!

22:00.510 --> 22:00.970
My Lady,

22:01.660 --> 22:03.560
she was just climbing
through the kitchen window

22:03.560 --> 22:05.090
when I caught her in the act.

22:05.510 --> 22:06.170
Sir, ma'am,

22:06.590 --> 22:08.790
take a look. Are these your belongings?

22:13.680 --> 22:15.610
We saved this meat for the New Year.

22:16.290 --> 22:17.420
And that hairpin...

22:17.510 --> 22:18.790
It seems to be Wang's.

22:19.480 --> 22:19.880
Right.

22:22.590 --> 22:23.650
Easy on her, Chu Wu.

22:23.680 --> 22:24.610
She's just a kid.

22:25.070 --> 22:25.350
Yes.

22:29.480 --> 22:30.160
Sir, ma'am,

22:31.430 --> 22:32.740
we bid you farewell.

22:33.110 --> 22:34.030
This thief is yours

22:34.030 --> 22:34.760
to deal with.

22:36.160 --> 22:36.640
Miss,

22:37.160 --> 22:38.760
I wanted to say this earlier,

22:39.270 --> 22:41.010
but this old fool stopped me.

22:41.270 --> 22:42.750
The authorities did issue a notice.

22:42.750 --> 22:44.550
But our village is quite remote,

22:44.920 --> 22:46.050
with the nearest inn

22:46.240 --> 22:47.640
situated over 30 li away.

22:48.070 --> 22:49.830
It's not safe for you three ladies

22:49.830 --> 22:50.920
to stay out there.

22:50.920 --> 22:51.480
Yes.

22:51.960 --> 22:53.360
Things have taken a turn.

22:53.880 --> 22:55.550
They caught a thief for us.

22:57.000 --> 22:58.460
Ladies, if you don't mind,

22:58.920 --> 23:00.650
please stay here for the night.

23:00.750 --> 23:02.440
You may leave tomorrow morning.

23:02.440 --> 23:03.070
Yes.

23:04.480 --> 23:05.080
Good idea.

23:05.790 --> 23:06.590
Thank you.

23:07.680 --> 23:09.080
Come on. Get in the house.

23:11.590 --> 23:12.000
Get up!

23:15.590 --> 23:15.920
Move.

23:30.830 --> 23:31.690
Your Highness.

23:33.240 --> 23:34.100
Your Highness?

23:35.960 --> 23:38.270
When I escorted the thief to the woodshed,

23:38.270 --> 23:39.480
she struggled too hard

23:39.480 --> 23:40.610
and made much noise,

23:40.640 --> 23:42.300
drawing some villagers over.

23:42.400 --> 23:44.720
Our host returned the lost items
to his neighbors.

23:44.720 --> 23:45.920
Now, about five to six households

23:45.920 --> 23:47.120
are aware of our stay.

23:50.830 --> 23:51.690
Your Highness,

23:51.920 --> 23:54.000
if we kill all those people
under the cover of darkness,

23:54.000 --> 23:55.530
we can frame the thief for it

23:55.920 --> 23:57.380
and then cover our tracks.

23:57.440 --> 23:57.880
No.

23:59.400 --> 23:59.930
Let's go.

24:00.270 --> 24:01.130
We should leave

24:01.590 --> 24:02.520
for Peiyang now.

24:05.350 --> 24:06.210
Your Highness,

24:06.440 --> 24:08.200
you're in no condition to go anywhere.

24:08.200 --> 24:09.800
You need a good night's rest.

24:10.270 --> 24:12.400
Chu Yi and Chu Si are keeping watch
on the roof.

24:12.400 --> 24:13.460
We don't have to run

24:13.750 --> 24:15.150
until anyone reports us.

24:16.030 --> 24:16.480
Fine.

24:17.880 --> 24:19.340
I'll sleep a bit more then.

24:19.680 --> 24:21.240
Wake me up in four hours.

24:22.110 --> 24:23.240
Yes, Your Highness.

24:28.940 --> 24:29.670
We found him!

24:35.070 --> 24:35.790
We found him,

24:35.790 --> 24:36.450
Centurion.

24:37.200 --> 24:37.800
Let me see.

24:40.680 --> 24:41.830
It really is him.

24:42.510 --> 24:44.030
Shall we notify the Imperial Guards?

24:44.030 --> 24:45.290
Are you stupid or what?

24:46.160 --> 24:48.200
He was caught by us, the Central Army.

24:48.200 --> 24:49.350
Bring a few men with you

24:49.350 --> 24:51.070
and escort him to His Highness.

24:51.070 --> 24:51.350
Yes!

24:52.480 --> 24:53.070
Take him away!

24:53.070 --> 24:53.330
Yes!

24:54.160 --> 24:54.490
Move!

24:58.590 --> 24:59.070
CEO Dan,

25:00.400 --> 25:01.060
wait for me.

25:02.240 --> 25:03.440
I'll be with you soon.

25:04.310 --> 25:05.170
Your Highness.

25:05.440 --> 25:06.300
Your Highness!

25:07.110 --> 25:07.970
Your Highness.

25:09.750 --> 25:10.610
Your Highness,

25:10.880 --> 25:12.480
there are soldiers here now.

25:14.750 --> 25:15.810
Search carefully!

25:16.590 --> 25:17.000
Move!

25:17.270 --> 25:18.440
-Officer, are you mistaken?
-Darn it!

25:18.440 --> 25:19.100
Officer...

25:19.240 --> 25:20.900
They got to this place so soon.

25:22.720 --> 25:23.050
Move!

25:25.510 --> 25:26.830
Cut the crap. Get a move on!

25:26.830 --> 25:27.480
Be quick!

25:28.310 --> 25:28.790
Search the house!

25:28.790 --> 25:29.520
Confess now!

25:30.920 --> 25:32.550
I don't know anything.

25:32.550 --> 25:34.830
-Walk faster!
-Report the household
with suspicious lodgers

25:34.830 --> 25:35.560
immdiately!

25:35.830 --> 25:37.440
The reward is10 tales of silver!

25:37.440 --> 25:37.750
Officer!

25:37.750 --> 25:38.070
Your Highness!

25:38.070 --> 25:39.720
-We're innocent!
-Your Highness!

25:39.720 --> 25:40.030
Move!

25:40.030 --> 25:41.290
Use the rear door here.

25:41.350 --> 25:41.880
Let's go.

25:42.200 --> 25:42.730
Go there!

25:44.400 --> 25:44.940
And you!

25:45.110 --> 25:46.040
-Hold on.
-Move!

25:50.920 --> 25:51.450
Quickly!

25:52.790 --> 25:53.550
Confess now!

25:56.750 --> 25:57.720
There are soldiers here.

25:57.720 --> 25:58.590
Run for your life.

25:58.590 --> 25:59.920
Don't steal again.

26:05.240 --> 26:05.770
This way.

26:07.680 --> 26:08.590
Check over there!

26:08.590 --> 26:08.920
Go!

26:13.030 --> 26:13.830
Open the door!

26:13.920 --> 26:14.620
Open up!

26:15.200 --> 26:15.720
Who is it?

26:15.720 --> 26:16.520
Open the door!

26:18.440 --> 26:18.880
Now!

26:22.480 --> 26:22.940
Search!

26:28.510 --> 26:29.370
Nobody's here.

26:29.590 --> 26:30.320
Where is she?

26:30.590 --> 26:32.520
Did you tip her off and let her go?

26:32.920 --> 26:34.620
Officer, we're innocent.

26:35.480 --> 26:36.030
Officer,

26:36.030 --> 26:37.830
we don't know who she really is.

26:37.920 --> 26:40.050
She only asked to spend the night here.

26:40.790 --> 26:42.640
-Officer, please spare our lives.
-Don't hurt us.

26:42.640 --> 26:43.170
Guys, go!

26:43.240 --> 26:44.400
Split up and search the village.

26:44.400 --> 26:44.930
Go, guys!

26:46.110 --> 26:46.550
Hurry!

26:51.940 --> 26:52.480
This way.

26:59.030 --> 26:59.890
It's a dead end.

27:00.310 --> 27:01.790
We need to first find an anchor up there

27:01.790 --> 27:03.850
and pull Your Highness up with a rope.

27:04.440 --> 27:05.240
It's too late.

27:05.830 --> 27:07.560
The soldiers will be here soon.

27:08.110 --> 27:08.640
Besides,

27:09.550 --> 27:10.610
how are we supposed

27:10.720 --> 27:12.320
to find a long rope right now?

27:12.510 --> 27:14.110
We'll lure the soldiers away

27:14.160 --> 27:15.590
to buy you as much time as possible.

27:15.590 --> 27:16.000
No.

27:17.160 --> 27:19.220
You escaped by the skin of your teeth.

27:19.680 --> 27:20.280
Going back

27:21.310 --> 27:22.970
is no different than suicide.

27:25.030 --> 27:26.290
Only I am their target.

27:26.640 --> 27:27.640
You should leave.

27:27.920 --> 27:29.240
I can't drag you down with me.

27:29.240 --> 27:30.240
Your Highness...

27:30.270 --> 27:30.930
Just leave.

27:31.350 --> 27:32.310
Don't worry, Your Highness.

27:32.310 --> 27:33.480
We'll use the trees for cover,

27:33.480 --> 27:34.640
take out some soldiers,

27:34.640 --> 27:36.030
and kill ourselves before capture.

27:36.030 --> 27:37.760
We'll make sure no clue is left.

27:39.550 --> 27:40.080
Exactly.

27:40.680 --> 27:41.480
Chu Wu, Chu Qi,

27:41.720 --> 27:42.450
think of a way

27:42.920 --> 27:44.850
to help Her Highness out of danger.

27:46.510 --> 27:46.880
Wait.

27:48.780 --> 27:49.910
What are your names?

27:50.200 --> 27:51.330
We don't have names.

27:51.350 --> 27:52.720
"Chu Yi" and "Chu Si" sound good enough.

27:52.720 --> 27:54.180
Take care, Your Highness.

27:55.440 --> 27:56.500
Do come back alive!

27:58.000 --> 27:58.860
Your Highness,

27:59.200 --> 28:00.200
death is almost certain.

28:00.200 --> 28:01.640
Might as well take a gamble.

28:01.640 --> 28:02.750
Chu Qi, stay alert.

28:02.970 --> 28:04.700
I'll go find an anchor up there.

28:10.790 --> 28:11.650
Your Highness,

28:11.830 --> 28:13.430
let's take a rest over there.

28:27.400 --> 28:29.200
I've been a liability to you all.

28:29.270 --> 28:31.470
Don't beat yourself up, Your Highness.

28:32.680 --> 28:33.410
Who's there?

28:55.790 --> 28:56.650
Your Highness,

28:56.960 --> 28:58.160
that hole's too small

28:58.160 --> 28:59.690
to fit more than two people.

28:59.750 --> 29:01.550
If she tries to harm you, I won't be able

29:01.550 --> 29:02.750
to rescue you in time.

29:03.790 --> 29:06.050
She could've reported me for the reward,

29:06.270 --> 29:08.130
yet she risked coming back for me.

29:09.350 --> 29:10.010
I trust her.

29:11.640 --> 29:12.880
You have great lightness skills.

29:12.880 --> 29:14.340
Hide on the cliff face now.

29:14.480 --> 29:15.000
Be careful.

29:15.000 --> 29:15.400
Got it.

29:36.830 --> 29:38.560
I saw them heading to the woods.

29:38.750 --> 29:40.080
Should we keep looking?

29:40.400 --> 29:41.530
Of course we should.

29:41.790 --> 29:43.830
If we catch her,
we'll receive a thousand taels of silver

29:43.830 --> 29:44.890
and be set for life.

29:46.110 --> 29:48.040
That woman's quite good at hiding.

29:48.670 --> 29:50.400
How many villages have we searched?

29:50.400 --> 29:51.640
I don't even get to enjoy the New Year.

29:51.640 --> 29:52.570
Don't be afraid.

29:53.200 --> 29:55.550
That's why she's called a demonic consort.

29:55.550 --> 29:56.510
The higher-ups

29:56.790 --> 29:57.550
told us to catch her,

29:57.550 --> 29:58.680
be she alive or dead.

29:59.030 --> 30:00.510
If she falls into our hands,

30:00.510 --> 30:02.840
let's take her to bed
like the Emperor did!

30:03.790 --> 30:04.650
-Let's go!
-Go!

30:04.680 --> 30:05.240
Check over there!

30:05.240 --> 30:05.770
Go, guys!

30:24.550 --> 30:25.880
You're unable to speak?

30:29.590 --> 30:30.520
Now I understand

30:31.400 --> 30:32.860
why you steal for a living.

31:03.160 --> 31:03.830
Xiahou Dan.

31:13.720 --> 31:15.440
Calling my name already, huh?

31:24.510 --> 31:25.740
"Being ill,

31:26.590 --> 31:28.960
the late Emperor felt
death was drawing near.

31:28.960 --> 31:32.680
This edict was therefore made
to pass the throne to the Crown Prince.

31:32.680 --> 31:34.540
But given the latter's minority,

31:35.310 --> 31:38.240
Prince Duan is vested
the power to govern as regent."

31:40.000 --> 31:40.930
Honorary titles

31:42.270 --> 31:43.550
are mere vanities.

31:44.200 --> 31:46.330
Pick whatever you like, Your Majesty.

31:48.000 --> 31:49.310
All is fine by me.

31:50.590 --> 31:52.630
Why don't you dress up
as the Empress Dowager

31:52.630 --> 31:53.860
in women's clothes?

31:55.070 --> 31:55.880
Xiahou Dan!

31:58.480 --> 31:59.680
I forgot it.

32:01.160 --> 32:02.430
You're scared of her.

32:02.880 --> 32:04.080
What did you just say?

32:15.720 --> 32:17.830
You knew clearly from the beginning

32:20.000 --> 32:21.720
who harmed your mother

32:23.920 --> 32:25.790
and you.

32:28.810 --> 32:31.140
But you had no choice
but to turn a blind eye

32:32.350 --> 32:33.860
and a deaf ear to the truth.

32:36.200 --> 32:38.060
You decided to vent all your anger

32:39.350 --> 32:42.070
on an innocent person.

32:44.920 --> 32:45.790
Why?

32:49.070 --> 32:51.110
Because you were too weak.

32:54.510 --> 32:56.770
You had to direct your hatred to someone,

32:57.000 --> 32:58.530
or you couldn't have lived.

33:00.160 --> 33:00.720
So,

33:02.000 --> 33:03.590
you picked a soft target—

33:07.100 --> 33:08.610
a headache sufferer,

33:10.920 --> 33:12.070
and a mere puppet.

33:14.350 --> 33:15.810
Luck was the entire reason

33:17.390 --> 33:19.570
that he ascended to the throne.

33:22.550 --> 33:24.170
Given that, you, Xiahou Bo,

33:24.750 --> 33:26.410
feel the urge to tell the world

33:27.480 --> 33:28.070
that you,

33:29.420 --> 33:30.410
Prince Duan,

33:33.270 --> 33:35.200
are better than him in every way,

33:36.550 --> 33:37.680
and that only you are

33:39.160 --> 33:41.240
meant to be the ruler.

33:55.990 --> 33:57.520
As a defeated loser

33:59.750 --> 34:01.000
behind bars,

34:01.000 --> 34:02.600
you're still talking tough.

34:05.420 --> 34:08.150
You're saying all this to provoke me,
aren't you?

34:09.040 --> 34:10.510
It won't work, Xiahou Dan.

34:12.150 --> 34:13.150
Stop struggling.

34:18.280 --> 34:20.080
I've hit a nerve with you, right?

34:20.150 --> 34:20.719
Shut up!

34:24.360 --> 34:25.219
Your Highness,

34:25.550 --> 34:26.480
I'll finish him.

34:27.070 --> 34:27.699
No need.

34:29.880 --> 34:32.080
Make sure you rough the late Emperor up.

34:33.480 --> 34:34.010
Remember

34:35.100 --> 34:36.900
to spare his right hand, though.

34:38.150 --> 34:40.190
He needs it to write his final edict.

34:53.900 --> 34:54.580
Yang, I...

34:56.110 --> 34:56.639
I...

34:57.840 --> 34:59.440
T-T-This is inappropriate.

35:02.550 --> 35:03.920
Er Lan, well, I...

35:04.360 --> 35:04.710
I...

35:05.510 --> 35:06.320
I didn't mean to intrude.

35:06.320 --> 35:08.120
I thought I entered Yang's room.

35:11.070 --> 35:12.610
This room is more spacious,

35:12.670 --> 35:14.440
making it easier to attend to Cen.

35:14.440 --> 35:16.050
So I swapped rooms with Yang this morning.

35:16.050 --> 35:16.710
Cen...

35:17.840 --> 35:18.240
Cen...

35:18.360 --> 35:19.490
Cen has arrived?

35:19.760 --> 35:20.280
Not yet.

35:20.550 --> 35:22.280
Yang has set off to receive him.

35:25.670 --> 35:26.760
Li, do you ever consider

35:26.760 --> 35:29.070
stop standing in the cold wind
by the door?

35:29.070 --> 35:30.880
We've been through life and death
together.

35:30.880 --> 35:32.540
Just forego the formalities.

35:44.230 --> 35:45.360
Were you just saying

35:46.440 --> 35:48.030
you had news about His Majesty?

35:48.030 --> 35:48.400
Yes.

35:50.710 --> 35:52.400
I waited at the palace gate all morning,

35:52.400 --> 35:53.860
but still couldn't get in.

35:54.000 --> 35:56.550
Nonetheless, a young eunuch
guarding the gate said

35:56.550 --> 35:59.760
Prince Duan summoned all ministers
to attend court tomorrow morning.

35:59.760 --> 36:01.200
He's just a prince.

36:01.590 --> 36:03.450
What right does he have to do that?

36:04.440 --> 36:05.670
I actually think it's a good thing.

36:05.670 --> 36:06.480
Hell no!

36:11.070 --> 36:12.270
My apologies, Er Lan.

36:12.670 --> 36:13.030
I...

36:13.670 --> 36:16.600
I've got used to it.
I keep forgetting that you are...

36:19.110 --> 36:21.090
In fact, I somewhat miss the time

36:21.710 --> 36:23.550
when you treated me like a man.

36:26.150 --> 36:27.460
We voiced our opinions

36:27.760 --> 36:29.880
and argued till we were red in the face,

36:29.880 --> 36:31.280
with the one and only focus

36:31.280 --> 36:33.280
on offering counsel to His Majesty.

36:33.280 --> 36:33.960
But now,

36:34.480 --> 36:35.320
Wang is gone.

36:36.030 --> 36:37.430
Her Highness is missing.

36:37.510 --> 36:39.240
His Majesty's fate is unknown.

36:39.710 --> 36:40.530
Given that,

36:40.630 --> 36:42.030
though this is not a fair request,

36:42.030 --> 36:43.360
I still have to ask you, Li,

36:43.360 --> 36:45.960
to continue to conceal my identity
for a while.

36:46.000 --> 36:47.800
Just treat me the same as before.

36:48.400 --> 36:48.730
Sure.

36:51.710 --> 36:52.170
I got it.

36:56.670 --> 36:57.600
I'll try my best.

37:09.800 --> 37:10.630
It has been

37:11.360 --> 37:13.620
three days since the Mount Bei incident.

37:13.760 --> 37:16.030
The city gate is sealed,
and so is the palace gate.

37:16.030 --> 37:17.630
We have no access to any news.

37:18.480 --> 37:20.070
So, our only chance lies in

37:20.960 --> 37:22.960
tomorrow's morning court session.

37:23.280 --> 37:23.630
Yes.

37:24.710 --> 37:26.040
You m-made a good point.

37:27.190 --> 37:28.920
But you're injured now, Er Lan.

37:29.070 --> 37:30.670
You shouldn't risk attending court
tomorrow.

37:30.670 --> 37:32.200
Just leave it to me and Yang.

37:32.840 --> 37:34.190
What is with you, Li?

37:34.190 --> 37:36.320
After just promising to keep my secret,

37:36.320 --> 37:37.780
you're giving it away now?

37:39.070 --> 37:39.510
I-I'm not.

37:39.510 --> 37:41.510
I haven't disclosed it to anyone...

37:41.710 --> 37:42.880
If I were a man,

37:42.880 --> 37:45.540
would I make a fuss
over a minor injury like this?

37:47.760 --> 37:48.030
Yes.

37:48.670 --> 37:49.070
Right.

37:49.920 --> 37:50.650
Although you

37:50.800 --> 37:51.590
and Her Highness

37:51.590 --> 37:52.280
are women,

37:52.590 --> 37:53.920
you two are incredibly formidable.

37:53.920 --> 37:54.880
I admire both of you.

37:54.880 --> 37:55.880
I tip my hat to you.

37:57.550 --> 37:59.810
Who am I to be compared with Her Highness?

38:01.630 --> 38:02.760
I wonder

38:03.510 --> 38:05.310
where Her Highness is right now.

38:10.400 --> 38:11.260
Your Highness!

38:13.270 --> 38:14.130
Your Highness.

38:14.400 --> 38:14.920
Your Highness,

38:14.920 --> 38:16.000
we made it back alive.

38:16.000 --> 38:16.800
Chu Yi, Chu Si.

38:17.190 --> 38:18.800
Why are you dressed as Imperial Guards?

38:18.800 --> 38:20.330
That gave me quite a fright!

38:22.190 --> 38:23.120
You're injured?

38:24.000 --> 38:25.760
If I hadn't knocked out
two Imperial Guards in the chaos

38:25.760 --> 38:27.020
and put on their armor,

38:27.360 --> 38:28.820
he would've lost his arm.

38:28.920 --> 38:30.710
Could those lousy fighters have wounded me

38:30.710 --> 38:31.630
if I hadn't took

38:31.790 --> 38:32.850
that blade for you?

38:33.100 --> 38:33.510
You...

38:33.630 --> 38:34.230
Cut it out.

38:34.670 --> 38:36.150
What's the situation like?

38:36.150 --> 38:37.070
Not good.

38:37.800 --> 38:39.710
People are searching everywhere
for Her Highness.

38:39.710 --> 38:42.040
We absolutely cannot take the main roads.

38:43.360 --> 38:44.800
But the distance between here

38:44.800 --> 38:46.260
and Peiyang is over 500 li.

38:47.280 --> 38:49.110
What route can we take
if not the main roads?

38:49.110 --> 38:50.590
After living in the palace for so long,

38:50.590 --> 38:52.990
we're not familiar with the roads outside.

39:08.670 --> 39:09.470
Do you mean...

39:09.990 --> 39:11.120
you can be our guide?

39:17.320 --> 39:18.250
You know the way?

39:20.360 --> 39:20.960
Terrific.

39:22.230 --> 39:22.630
But...

39:23.760 --> 39:25.180
you might get in danger

39:25.280 --> 39:26.480
for sticking with us.

39:26.590 --> 39:27.850
Will you still join us?

39:34.960 --> 39:35.960
You want payment?

39:41.550 --> 39:41.960
Chu Wu,

39:42.030 --> 39:43.090
give her some food.

39:43.640 --> 39:44.240
By the way,

39:44.590 --> 39:46.050
I don't know your name yet.

39:51.400 --> 39:52.600
You don't have a name?

39:55.960 --> 39:57.070
Why do none of you

39:57.550 --> 39:58.630
have names?

40:03.630 --> 40:04.090
Well...

40:05.550 --> 40:07.010
How about I give you a name?

40:11.670 --> 40:12.530
Let me think...

40:23.190 --> 40:23.990
We'll call you

40:24.400 --> 40:25.000
"Flower."

40:25.190 --> 40:25.650
What do you think?
